      "content": "Hey Marcus,\n\nFirst off, I want to say that your technical skills during our final interview were absolutely stellar, and it was a pleasure meeting you. We were genuinely impressed by your talent and the way you approached our problem-solving challenges.\n\nHowever, after careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with another candidate who has slightly more specific experience with our current cloud architecture. We know this is tough news, especially since you were such a strong fit, but we want to be firm that this decision is final.\n\nWe truly appreciate the time you took to interview with us and the effort you put into the process. We hope you understand that we are looking for the best possible fit for this specific role, and we wish you the very best in your job search.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]\nHiring Team",
